How to handle PREFIX/share/joomla/tmp, PREFIX/share/joomla/cache and
PREFIX/share/joomla/administrator/cache? Most likely these should be
somewhere in /var (e.g. /var/joomla).

This package has known vulnerabilities, please investigate and fix if possible.
	see: 	http://developer.joomla.org/security/news/283-20081101-core-comcontent-xss-vulnerability.html
		http://developer.joomla.org/security/news/284-20081102-core-comweblinks-xss-vulnerability.html
